<span class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface uppercase tracking-widest block mb-4 border-t border-[#2D2926] border-opacity-10 pt-4 w-12">A note on the name.</span>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md italic text-on-surface-variant">We chose a word that felt like the snap of the cracker itself. Crispness is a universal language, needing no translation in the kitchen.</p>
</div>
