<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg italic text-on-surface-variant text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                "We built Sprod-Kraaks not to be the biggest, but to be the uncompromising best. We refuse to speed up the process. We refuse to use cheaper oils. If that means we make less, we make less. But what we make is true."
            </p>
